    <td colspan="3" align="left" valign="top" scope="row"><div class="strapline">Welcome to the School of Electronics and Computer Science</div>
	<p>Information about the School, including admissions to <a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20060511135728/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/admissions/ug/">undergraduate</a> and <a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20060511135728/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/admissions/pg/">postgraduate</a> programmes, is available from the links at the top of this page. Starting from here, you can find latest news, hottest topics, <a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20060511135728/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/news/researcher-profiles.php">researcher profiles</a>, background features, <a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20060511135728/http://eprints.ecs.soton.ac.uk/">publications</a> …and more…</p>
