              International Conference on<br />
              Automatic Face and Gesture Recognition</a>. Co-chaired by our Professor <a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20060511135728/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/people/msn">Mark Nixon</a>   with Professor Joseph Kittler from Surrey. The conference  is being attended by over 150 delegates from around the world.<br />
